    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <div class="about-container span_7_of_12">
      <p>We want to give restaurant owners a smart marketing tool that reaches the right audience at the right time. Dinner Winner users tell us when they're hungry, what neighborhood they want to dine in, and how many people are in their party.  If you're located in their desired neighborhood, you'll be given the opportunity to bid on their patronage with your own unique offers.  Proactively bring in business with Mass Deals that can be offered daily.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
